=== Asismel amensay ===
Deg usismel amzikan (aqbur), amedya deg wagla n  [[Johannes Thiele]] (1929-1935), llan 3 n [[adu-smil|idu-smilen]] ibuda: 

* [[Ifeckdaten]] (''Prosobranchia''): d iɣersiwen [[ilel|iwlalen]], lan (sɛan) [[Afuck|iɣenwazen]] deg tazwara (zdat) n tfekka s udem n wul.
* [[Ifeckdfiren]] (''Opisthobranchia''): Yakk nsen d iwlalen, lan (sɛan) [[afuck]] (iɣenwazen) s deffir n tfekka, Am [[tiferdarin]] (''Pteropoda'') i [[Assezgi|yessezgen]] ar tudert tassuflant.
* [[Tinturin]] (''Pulmonata''): Ilan (yesɛan) [[turin]] (aberfiw) deg yideg n ifecka maca kra deg-sent (am [[Alemnis|ilemnisen]]) uɣalen ar tudert deg waman.

